<h2>Bootstrap Buttons / drop downs</h2>
<p>
    So the long and short of it is that:<br />
    1. the container element (ie the toggler's parent) must have 'dropdown' as class or data attribute<br />
    2. the toggler must have 'dropdown-toggle' class<br />
    3. the ul must be next to the toggler and have 'dropdown-menu' class
</p>
